{"tid":430028,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"小米首部 18:9 全屏幕入門機, 紅米 Note 5 真機曝光","createTime":"2017-10-09T12:38:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T11:26:51.000Z","uid":52215,"like":6,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"d94d96364ecab323572840850afd5f10c9e4c269","tid":430028,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:38:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/203821_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F203821_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=60159f86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/09/203825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F09%2F203825_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=76a9d180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全屏幕設計可謂下年手機市場的主流, 而這股風氣變變延至到其他品牌的中低階機, 作為性價比的始祖小米手機, 究竟何時會在國內發布全屏幕的入門機呢? 這的確是好影響採用全屏幕設計手機的普及程度!<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n昨日有網友公開了疑似紅米 Note 5 真機圖, 而比較意外的事該機採用18:9全屏幕設計, 屏幕上下邊框非常窄! 至於機背方面基本承繼了紅米 Note 系列的傳統; 按照以往紅米 Note 系列的定價, 呢部機嘅定價可能只是千幾。<br />\n<br />\n至於規格方面, 不同消息均指出紅米 Note 5 不會搭載驍龍660, 而最大可能是 MTK Helio P25 處理器, 主鏡頭為1600萬像+500萬像, 電池容量為4000 mAh, 至於售價方面, 3GB+16GB 版定價 999 CNY, 折合港元 $1173, 3+32GB 則是1299CNY, 折合港元 $1526, 而4GB +64GB 則為1699 CNY, 折合港元 1996。"},{"pid":"bcfa9f344ffe64027fa95de2ce5733fbb0d91de8","tid":430028,"uid":51978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:40:16.000Z","msg":"認真 香港應該好多阿叔阿嬸會買返部"},{"pid":"90acc59b05ddce17796f96f6da954ab72e7958a2","tid":430028,"uid":8171,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T12:41:14.000Z","msg":"其實18:9同2:1有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f3